summary: ENDGAME SPOILER ALERT
title: ENDGAME SPOILER ALERT
body:
A few hours after all the surviving Avengers return to the complex, Bucky finds Peter sitting on the couch on Tony’s floor, curled up in a tiny ball. He sits down next to him and they sit in silence.

Then Peter turns to Bucky, tears in his eyes, and asks in a scratchy, worn voice, “Why does it feel so big in here now, Mr Winter Soldier?”

And Bucky smiles a sad smile. “Because they’re not here to comfort us, kid.” Peter just bursts into tears and Bucky wraps his arms around him, swallowing his own tears, determined to be strong for Peter and for Steve.
